public abstract class AppResourcePreCommitActionTypeBOMImpl
extends BusinessObjectModuleImpl
implements PreCommitActionTypeBOM

The CTM infrastructure will call the PreCommitActionType BOM API once for the given business object type. As part of a change set transport, application resource records may be inserted, updated or deleted. When such operations occur, the client resources and server properties resource caches must be refreshed. This class is responsible for refreshing these caches.

preCommit

public void preCommit(java.util.Set<BusinessObjectActionData> businessObjectActionDataSet)
               throws AppException,
                      InformationalException
The CTM infrastructure calls this function to refresh the client resources and server properties caches after all of the AppResource BOM instances have been applied as part of a change set.

Specified by:
